      {
        "type": "narrative",
        "heading": "What This Means for Residents",
        "body": "This change demonstrates a shift towards more sustainable living. The drop in waste means less strain on disposal systems and possibly, a cleaner environment. For residents, it aligns with a broader movement of reducing environmental footprints."
